OL,3,CMan hit in groin with brick during
OL,4,CSouthport riots jailed for over two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA man, seen in a viral video being hit
OL,8,Fin the groin with a brick during the
OL,9,Fsummer's Southport riots, has been
OL,10,Fjailed for over two years.
OL,12,FBrian Spencer was seen on the video
OL,13,Fclip taunting police, as they were
OL,14,Fpelted with stones and bricks.
OL,16,FThe 40-year-old is then hit by a
OL,17,Fwayward missile in the head and
OL,18,Fseconds later takes a brick to the
OL,19,Fcrotch.
