OL,4,CSouthport riots jailed for over two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe clip of the incident was shared
OL,8,Fwidely on social media.
OL,10,FOn Monday, Spencer, of Lytham Road,
OL,11,FSouthport, appeared at Liverpool Crown
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FHe was jailed for two years and six
OL,15,Fmonths after admitting violent
OL,16,Fdisorder on 30 July.
