OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FHe was also jailed after admitting
OL,8,Fracially/religiously aggravated
OL,9,Fharassment, which relates to a
OL,10,Fseparate incident the following day at
OL,11,FSouthport Hospital.
OL,13,FSpencer verbally abused another
OL,14,Fpatient while receiving treatment for
OL,15,Fthe injuries he sustained during the
OL,16,Fdisorder.
OL,18,FHe was caught on footage from the day
OL,19,Fpunching a police vehicle several
OL,20,Ftimes and picking up and throwing
OL,21,Fwheelie bins at officers.
