OL,7,FLater that evening, officers were
OL,8,Fcalled to a separate incident where
OL,9,FSpencer was in attendance, and took
OL,10,Fhim to hospital for treatment to the
OL,11,Fhead injury he had sustained during
OL,12,Fthe disorder.
OL,14,FThe officers recognised him from the
OL,15,Fviral social media footage and he was
OL,16,Farrested.
OL,18,FLiverpool Crown Court heard how he
OL,19,Fracially abused another patient while
OL,20,Freceiving treatment for his injuries.
