OL,3,CMan hit in groin with brick during
OL,4,CSouthport riots jailed for over two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FNationwide trouble broke out across
OL,8,Fthe UK the day after three girls were
OL,9,Fkilled in a knife attack in Southport.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Paula Jones, of
OL,12,FMerseyside Police, said: "The actions
OL,13,Fof the people who took part in the
OL,14,Fdisorder was extremely serious and
OL,15,Fmany officers were injured during the
OL,16,Fdespicable scenes as bricks, bins and
OL,17,Fother missiles were thrown at them.
OL,19,F"Spencer was involved in the violence
OL,20,Fand will now spend a significant
OL,21,Famount of time in prison.
