OL,7,F"We continue to review footage and
OL,8,Finformation as it comes in, and we
OL,9,Fwill not stop until we've put everyone
OL,10,Fwe possibly can before the courts."
OL,12,FThe total number of people arrested by
OL,13,FMerseyside Police has now reached 163,
OL,14,Fwith 117 charged and 88 sentenced to
OL,15,F182 years and four months.
